description: Come join the DragonFire Family Mon/Wed/Fri at 2:00 PM for a mixed calisthenics and weightlifting workout. Monday's and Friday's will focus on calisthenics and Wednesday's will be specifically weightlifting at the outdoor gym next to the bar park.
Skills focused workouts that combine strength training and skill drills

Join the president of TritonThenix this quarter for our diverse lineup of bodyweight-focused workouts, open to all skill levels! Whether you're new to calisthenics or a seasoned athlete, these sessions are designed to help you build strength, increase endurance, and develop flexibility while having fun!
Start training calisthenics with the King family. Fundamentals + Muscle Ups + Handstands + Front Lever + More
